## Using Maven with AspectJ 8: MASPECTJ or MaJ

The running project, a part of https://github.com/kodcu/aspectj-ebook[the AspectJ E-Book], shows the basic integration between Maven 3.x.x and AspectJ 1.8.3.

**Technologies:**

1.	Java 8
2.	AspectJ 8
	
### What's included:

