	\---main
	   +---aspect
	   |   \---com
	   |       \---kodcu
	   |           \---app
	   |               \---aspects
	   |                       DataAspect.aj
	   |                       SoftenedHandlerAspect.aj
	   |                       SystemStructure.aj
	   |                       TraceAspect.aj
	   |                       ValidationAspect.aj
	   |
	   +---java
